埋怨, 食野又埋怨添, 日日彈呢度唔好果度差...<br />\n小事上解釋下就算吧, 畢竟佢地見識少, 要教導一下, 你都唔好睇得太重, 影響旅行心情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1226ec9eaa8385cace8c8038c0771c74d2d2a3a","tid":881173,"uid":49004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ed881cad225c9f02a0ef571e33773cf531d38dda","tid":881173,"uid":172306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T14:39:11.000Z","msg":"可能係冇你去泰國叫雞咁好玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T01:15:13.000Z","msg":"幻幻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a69657bfd1ee573da1184838f1a757562271ee47","tid":881173,"uid":50500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T02:48:59.000Z","msg":"家父 麻撚煩 炎三炎四 無主見求撚其<br />\n家母 雞 牛  羊 魚生唔食得<br />\n家姐 無錢 失業多年 同兩老關係差<br />\n我 無女 係咁多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc4a107584945c4f8062ed237ab57ed98ff18e4d","tid":881173,"uid":5038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T03:14:54.000Z","msg":"最慘係兩老覺得d價錢好平<br />\n好似旺季聖誕去日本咁,一早明言機票酒店一個人都成皮萬銀<br />\n老豆成日話 幾百蚊就張機票啦, 佢話佢book機票<br />\n搞搞下又嫌貴個d, 又話唔去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n去到旅行 條撚屌又要成日食煙又盛<br />\n失禮死人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔係我唔想同兩老去旅行 而加老豆你知唔知自己好撚麻煩<br />\n以後跟團去算"},{"pid":"1df2312d0818f896f9ebf5eac079af440467e1f9","tid":881173,"uid":45616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T03:17:52.000Z","msg":"我呀媽飛得仲多過我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f76eae82e0b94f079d058bb16809013f8cecc85","tid":881173,"uid":38623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f2d5fd9159343b6aa2269c843a8ba1055c3267e9","tid":881173,"uid":190739,"like":12,"dislike"